import React from 'react'
import salom from '../../RASIM/sr.png'
import {Conatainer ,Logotip,Search,Store,LogoTitle,Logo,Input} from './style'
const Navabr = () => {
    return (
        <Conatainer>

            <Logotip>
                 <Logo src={salom}/>
                 <LogoTitle>Furniking</LogoTitle>
            </Logotip>

            <Search>
                  <Input  placeholder="Search here"/>
                  <select>
                       <option>Categories</option>
                       <option>react</option>
                       <option>jquery</option>
                       <option>vue</option>
                  </select>
            </Search>

            <Store>xayir</Store>
        </Conatainer>
    )
}

export default Navabr
